Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！从森林那边来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师大人 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是四魂碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师大人 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让蜈蚣突然变得凶暴的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么事情尽管叫我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师大人 谢礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我收下这个就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是从我们村里出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师 珊瑚登场！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上有好多星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些星星的数量和四魂碎片的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个比较多呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来前面还有很长一段路要走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那混蛋也跟我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在收集着四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还可以省下不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让那家伙去收集 然后我们一拼抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个计划不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到的四魂碎片越多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落就会变得更强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时候就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们得抢先收集更多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种小孩子都懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么就不懂呢？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脑子到底有多蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收集到所有碎片以后有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要变成真正的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不够强就什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算遇到看不顺眼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不够人家强的话就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你藉助四魂之玉的力量变成完全的妖怪以后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能保持自我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过有谁用四魂碎片的力量做好事的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到四魂之玉之力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 也会失去心智
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得自己说过要变成好妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你想要保护戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你利用四魂之玉变成妖怪之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能就会把戈薇小姐和七宝吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都要吃？就不吃弥勒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一早逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在为止跟四魂之玉扯上关系的妖怪们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就都不是好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为那样罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我…不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人把四魂碎片拿走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候拿走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！快说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有妖怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去找除妖师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大蜈蚣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里像了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说除妖师？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有人以除妖为职业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个除妖师在收集四魂之玉的碎片吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她还说那个叫什么的玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从她的村子流落出去的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你知道这件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有四魂之玉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已经由桔梗在守护着了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉是怎么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎物是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带回来一些脚和皮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用来制作盔甲吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖哦 乖哦 云母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有做好孩子啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首领叫你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你得到四魂碎片了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样能镇住碎片的邪气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概50年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把玉交给一位灵力高强的巫女保管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并由她净化着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那位大人最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是在争抢玉的战斗中去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在找到能够净化玉的灵力高强的人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把碎片收集到村里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并小心守护了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净化玉的灵力…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就又有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 你也要做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经11岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该参加实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪真的会喷火喷毒的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 你害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才没害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要收拾的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是一些大蛇和大蜘蛛罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可怕的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伪装成人类的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种妖怪要是得到四魂之玉就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师 你们来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只大蜘蛛每晚都会来袭击城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城中已经有数人被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有办法收拾它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请交给我们处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从村里挑选了几个高手来除妖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你说的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是像女人一样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小孩子都有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在下的女儿和儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们村是数一数二的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就请您见识他们的身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没？要加油哦 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…父亲这个大骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公 它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有妖怪出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主的病之所以久治不愈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因为妖怪的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公已经找来了除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场喧闹也只到今夜为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后只需期待少主您早日康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它围起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 压制住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为珊瑚是村里最好的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就把那个大蜘蛛给…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它脑袋打烂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是块头大了点 没什么了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太简单了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只蜘蛛的妖气也很弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 为什么要把父亲他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…连我都不认识了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 除妖师！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随他们去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有趣的余兴节目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝…是蜘蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对姐弟都发疯了 杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射下一箭 对准发疯的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥…琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕…有我在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两姐弟和好了啊 可喜可贺可喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主…主公…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 主公他到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得父亲不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是被妖怪附身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜了那些除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们埋到庭院一角去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然没一个人知道除妖师的村落在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道在山里面啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 总之去找就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你要去除妖师的村子抢四魂碎片吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别反而被除掉了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 人家似乎是专业高手诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我也很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉为何会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还说四魂之玉本来就出自他们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也一定很想知道原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…真是让人讨厌的风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么正在接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且数量很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一大群妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强的妖气…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一般的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 诡异得让人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们想去攻击什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对除妖师姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看看还很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么…能死…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女除妖师？你还活着啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们多年来对除妖师的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎都发泄完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好心告诉你们这个山寨的除妖师都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们居然连我都想攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知好歹的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山寨？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那些妖怪的目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟妖怪战斗过了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们一直在找的除妖师的村落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没有四魂碎片的气息呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上去追的话说不定能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把这些村民埋葬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妖怪活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个声音是犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静下来 云母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人不是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想念您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥加爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认识啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是犬夜叉的家臣 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这里是除妖师隐居的村落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎世世代代都是除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪那些妖怪会这么怨恨他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是偏偏趁这个时候来袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的高手都被召入城中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好是村子的防御最薄弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心里面一直觉得很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召入城中的人们没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少还有你一个人活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不回答少主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做珊瑚对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲 还有弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和同伴都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听从您的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快马加鞭 赶到了除妖师的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到村子里的人都被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本来还想向村里人打听许多事情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指四魂之玉的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是在这里调查玉的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早以前就十分在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉到底是什么东西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为跟玉扯上关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后都会遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪着四魂之玉的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后就来到了这个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有一件事我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中一直都能看到一个白狒狒的身影出没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白狒狒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落…他就在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把详细情况告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在除妖师的村落看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了横尸遍野的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和袭击村子的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉企图利用四魂之玉的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成完全的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能他认为能在除妖师的村落得到四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会袭击那个村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:22:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个袭击村子的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去杀了那个叫犬夜叉的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们在生命的旅程中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}逐渐失去一切
